        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is a personal brand and why does it matter?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "A personal brand is the specific, consistent impression you create in the minds of people who encounter your work, your name, or your public presence. It matters because it determines which opportunities find you, what compensation you can command, and how much leverage you have in career negotiations." }
        },
