          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How do you build a personal brand without being inauthentic?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Authentic personal branding starts with identifying what you genuinely know, care about, and do better than most people — then communicating those things consistently over time. It is not performance or persona construction; it is deliberate amplification of what is already genuinely true about you." }
        },
